    <Teaser>Updates all City State type bonuses to work as in the Ethiopia Pack.</Teaser>
    <Authors>JNR</Authors>
	<SpecialThanks>P0kiehl; SeelingCat; Firaxis (Ethiopia DLC Team)</SpecialThanks>
